text: The IV CELAC summit or 2016 CELAC summit was the fourth ordinary heads of state summit of the Community of Latin American and Caribbean States. It was held on 26 and 27 January 2016 in Quito, Ecuador. == References == == External links == * Official declaration * Official declaration (Spanish) Category:2016 conferences Category:2016 in international relations Category:2016 in South America Category:2016 in the Caribbean Category:Diplomatic conferences in Ecuador Summit,2016
